OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779127867
OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,FAn MP has claimed that Royal Mail
OL,7,Fstaff were told to empty a busy
OL,8,Fsorting office before she visited to
OL,9,Fgive the false impression that it was
OL,10,Fnot dealing with backlogs.
OL,12,FMelanie Onn went to the office in her
OL,13,FGreat Grimsby and Cleethorpes
OL,14,Fconstituency following complaints of
OL,15,Fdelivery delays.
OL,17,FThe Labour MP said when she arrived
OL,18,Fmail frames and portable cages were
OL,19,Fempty and "all operations seemed to be
OL,20,Fgoing exceptionally smoothly without
OL,21,Fany problems whatsoever".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779127867
OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,FBut she has now written to the small
OL,7,Fbusiness minister after being told by
OL,8,Fpost workers that managers had issued
OL,9,Finstructions to clear the office "to
OL,10,Fdemonstrate that there were no
OL,11,Fproblems, nothing to see here".
OL,13,FRoyal Mail said the claims were
OL,14,F"simply not true".
OL,16,FMs Onn said she visited the office on
OL,17,F1 May after raising concerns about
OL,18,Fdisruption caused by large volumes of
OL,19,Fparcels and a "substantial backlog" of
OL,20,Fmail.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779127867
OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,FIn her letter to small business
OL,7,Fminister Blair McDougall, she wrote:
OL,8,F"I had also heard that some delivery
OL,9,Frounds have gone undelivered for up to
OL,10,Fnine days, with post left in the
OL,11,Foffice day after day.
OL,13,F"There was frustration that parcels
OL,14,Fwere being prioritised despite staff
OL,15,Freportedly being advised that this
OL,16,Fshould not be the case, leaving
OL,17,Fletters and important documents
OL,18,Fundelivered."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779127867
OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,FWhen she visited, she said, she was
OL,7,Fgiven a "different impression" and
OL,8,Ffelt her visit was "entirely
OL,9,Funnecessary".
OL,11,FBut she added: "Since then, I happen
OL,12,Fto have had conversations with a
OL,13,Fnumber of post workers while they've
OL,14,Fbeen out on their rounds.
OL,16,F"They each independently disclosed
OL,17,Fthat management instructions on the
OL,18,Fday of my visit told them to clear the
OL,19,Fframes of post and take it out of the
OL,20,Foffice. Some of the mail remained
OL,21,Funsorted in the boxes.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779127867
OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,F"The intention was to show a clear
OL,7,Foffice, and demonstrate that there
OL,8,Fwere no problems, nothing to see here.
OL,10,F"However, every single one of the
OL,11,Fpostmen I spoke to all independently
OL,12,Fcorroborated that the mail removed
OL,13,Fthat day, reappeared at their frames
OL,14,Fon the Tuesday morning following the
OL,15,Fbank holiday weekend.
OL,17,F"This meant they then had four days'
OL,18,Fworth of mail waiting for them that
OL,19,Fmorning."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779127867
OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,FMs Onn has called for Royal Mail to be
OL,7,Fhonest about its challenges.
OL,9,FRoyal Mail denied the claims.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "These claims are
OL,12,Fsimply not true. We invite MPs into
OL,13,Four delivery offices so they can see
OL,14,Fthe operation for themselves.
OL,16,F"Mail goes out for delivery in the
OL,17,Fmorning, so offices are naturally
OL,18,Fquieter in the afternoon. That is not
OL,19,Fevidence that mail has been removed or
OL,20,Fhidden.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
