OL,3,CClaims post was hidden before MP's
OL,4,Cvisit to sorting office
OL,6,F"We closely track service performance
OL,7,Facross our network, which is how we
OL,8,Fknow more than 92% of letters are
OL,9,Fdelivered on time. We also carry out
OL,10,Faround 100 unannounced spot checks
OL,11,Fevery week to check mail is being
OL,12,Fmanaged properly."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
